<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Approved by the 1970 <a href="/wiki/World_Conference_(Community_of_Christ)" title="World Conference (Community of Christ)">World Conference</a>.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-29"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Included in the LDS <a href="/wiki/Pearl_of_Great_Price_(Latter_Day_Saints)" class="mw-redirect" title="Pearl of Great Price (Latter Day Saints)">Pearl of Great Price</a> as <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/pgp/moses/7">Moses chapter 7</a>.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Approved by the 1970 <a href="/wiki/World_Conference_(Community_of_Christ)" title="World Conference (Community of Christ)">World Conference</a>; Genesis 7:1–78 in the <a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith_Translation_of_the_Bible" title="Joseph Smith Translation of the Bible">Inspired Version of the Bible</a>.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-31"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-31">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20170624015041/http://www.cofchrist.org/Common/Cms/resources/Documents/World-Conference/2016-Conference-Official-Actions.pdf">"Official Actions of the 2016 World Conference"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>Community of Christ</i>. 11 June 2016. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cofchrist.org/common/cms/resources/Documents/World-Conference/2016-Conference-Official-Actions.pdf">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> on 24 June 2017<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">19 December</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Community+of+Christ&amp;rft.atitle=Official+Actions+of+the+2016+World+Conference&amp;rft.date=2016-06-11&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cofchrist.org%2Fcommon%2Fcms%2Fresources%2FDocuments%2FWorld-Conference%2F2016-Conference-Official-Actions.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADoctrine+and+Covenants" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
